{"tid":2073001,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] HardDisk 搬去第二台機, 但USER folder無權限, 應該點搞","createTime":"2020-06-21T04:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T15:23:42.000Z","uid":123988,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1d61da2f494f5a645d0b06c0d29b798614f1908a","tid":2073001,"uid":123988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"本身係 Notebook, 買左個 2.5吋既盒<br />\n而家係另一台機已經睇到之前啲FILE<br />\n但係重要既文件放左係 User/[user name] 入面<br />\n*** 重要相, 真係好怕唔見 ***<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我上網搵左 有右鍵 -&gt; 安全性 - &gt; 改 owner , 但我見好慢<br />\n又有 <br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">takeown /f f:\\ /r /d y</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">takeown /f f:\\ /a /r /d y</code></pre><br />\n見只係 cmd 版, 我怕都係咁慢, 或者整壞啲FILE<br />\n<br />\n又有人話<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">convert X: /FS:NTFS /NoSecurity</code></pre><br />\n話可以變成 無安全性<br />\n<br />\n有無CHING 有經驗點搞 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7825a140a60d9b4df516b9d30c0c5898a59ee08c","tid":2073001,"uid":172677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:50:44.000Z","msg":"你搬野嗰陣 佢有冇問你取得管理者授權？"},{"pid":"820f164218ed3a478b91c0103700802116a16d06","tid":2073001,"uid":43178,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢第二台機"},{"pid":"bbf1d2117e2991a21efccacbe0e26ba0b9e6ade1","tid":2073001,"uid":70313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"放落USB/ Google Drive好似安全啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e5761bf6bef549620e14db27fa157a94d571cc","tid":2073001,"uid":5159,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T07:01:49.000Z